{"type": "article", "id": 25006, "title": "伞架", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-06T07:19:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152311dB4lWxtDXGIHf0hz.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是三星推出的一个伞架的概念设计，它有上下两个缺口分别放直杆雨伞和折叠雨伞，伞架的凹槽可以聚集雨伞流过的水并干燥。它更重要的设计是上面的天气情况显示屏，有天气预报的功能，提醒你该拿伞了。伞架的两侧是不完全对称的曲线轮廓，有助于凸显轻盈和现代感。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152303DCOGkW3j4r9Jzgt1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215230446cN7vRtiLpO2JXV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152309pqJILVcrQ5AHxBOt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152309hsVRxyUdbm1Tq6tJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152310AQk10CPWb8RdZ6cg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}